Package nz.ac.wgtn.swen225.lc.domain

Class Domain

java.lang.Object
nz.ac.wgtn.swen225.lc.domain.Domain
Direct Known Subclasses:
Domain.StateClass
public class Domain extends Object
Represents the game domain, handling game state and game entities. This class follows the Singleton pattern.
